{"tid":1308080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"面對公屋毀牆藍絲嘅朋友，要記得亂拋垃圾即扣五分","createTime":"2019-07-11T20:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T20:03:46.000Z","uid":260806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03edcc872b00d72a2867cd09f42237d386864549","tid":1308080,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T20:03:46.000Z","msg":"亂拋垃圾<br />\n<br />\n隨地棄置垃圾，如棄置於電梯大堂或無蓋垃圾桶內等<br />\n<br />\n在屋邨公共地方吸煙或攜帶燃著的香煙<br />\n<br />\n即時扣五分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/estate-management/marking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic-housing%2Festate-management%2Fmarking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement%2Findex.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0EXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=3fa2d4ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/tc/public-housing/estate-management/marking-scheme-for-estate-management-enforcement/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n兩年扣夠十六分就要交屋"}]}